flowchart LR
    subgraph Frontend
        UI[User Interface]
    end

    subgraph Backend Modules
        CSVP[CSV Processor]
        SCANE[Scanner Engine]
        PLAY[Playwright Engine]
        DETE[Detection Engine]
        CONF[Confidence Scoring]
        DBL[Database Layer]
        EXPS[Export System]
    end

    UI -->|upload CSV| CSVP
    CSVP -->|normalized domains| DBL
    DBL -->|scan queue| SCANE
    SCANE --> PLAY
    PLAY -->|captured evidence| DETE
    DETE --> CONF
    CONF -->|scores + evidence| DBL
    DBL -->|results| UI
    UI -->|filter + star + tag| DBL
    UI -->|export request| EXPS
    EXPS -->|query filtered results| DBL
    EXPS -->|file| UI
